33
00:03:19,365 --> 00:03:21,333
I don't use the cane,
you're shocked.
I use the cane...

34
00:03:21,401 --> 00:03:22,493
We're just concerned.

35
00:03:22,569 --> 00:03:24,662
About the wrong person.
I can breathe.

36
00:03:24,737 --> 00:03:26,796
Ezra Powell,
on the other hand,
is gonna die.

37
00:03:26,873 --> 00:03:28,636
The Ezra Powell?
The researcher?

38
00:03:28,708 --> 00:03:29,902
The guy who wrote
that textbook?

39
00:03:29,976 --> 00:03:31,568
"That" textbook?
The textbook.

40
00:03:31,644 --> 00:03:34,044
Wait. There's actually
another doctor you admire?

41
