Of course, most of them
look a lot better in
knee socks than Ezra Powell,

43
00:03:39,953 --> 00:03:41,352
but seeing as they
can all breathe...

44
00:03:41,421 --> 00:03:44,254
CHASE: Oxygenation is
through the floor
and lungs are full of fluid.

45
00:03:44,324 --> 00:03:45,791
Gotta be his heart.

46
00:03:45,892 --> 00:03:46,881
Could be amyloidosis.

47
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:50,452
Or his lungs, probably from
years of inhaling
toxic chemicals in his lab.

48
00:03:50,530 --> 00:03:52,657
CHASE: It's not the lungs.
The chest x-ray's clean.

49
